      ***ALGR02*****************************************************************
      *  OQ INPROCESS SCAN                                                     *
      *
      * TCHK  07/12/11 CREATE
      * TCHK1 08/31/12 CHG GET MATERIAL & KANBAN READ
      * TCHK2 04/07/15 RMV 2ND SHIFT
      * T.SAKAKI 07/13/15 ADD OQ7   %0001
      * LEC      01/20/17  CHANGE TO ACCEPT INPUT OF ALL KANBANS BEFORE WRITING
JW1   * JW       04/27/18  ADD SUB# TO MESSAGE
      * LEC      05/8/18  COPY FROM ALGR01. ALGR01 USE LINE PRTR, ALGR02 USE
      *          LASER AND NEED BAR CODE. ALGPR02 PRINTS ON PREPRINTED FORM.
JW2   * JW       05/14/18  ADD DATE CHECK
      * LEC      06/28/18  ADD LANPRT32 TO PRINTER SELECTION
LC1   * LEC      11/11/19  CHG TO ACCEPT QR BARCODE OR STANDARD BC
      **************************************************************************
     FALGPW02TCF  E                    WORKSTN
     FALBPL30 IF  E           K        DISK
     FFCEPL07 IF  E           K        DISK
TCHK1FFCETL06 IF  E           K        DISK
     FADHTL05 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAB#PPCT UF  E           K        DISK                      A
      *
     FALGPP01 IF  E           K        DISK                      A
     FALGPP11 IF  E           K        DISK                      A
      *
     FALGPR02 O   E                    PRINTER                        UC
      **************************************************************************
     E                    ERR     1  20 17
     E                    CMD     1   1 75
     E                    ARY        75  1
     E                    LOT         4  8
     E                    KAN         4 15
      **************************************************************************
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      * SYSTEM TIME
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WSDT
     I                                        1   60WSSTM6
     I                                        1   40WSSTM4
     I                                        1   20WSSHHH
     I                                        3   40WSSNNN
     I                                        5   60WSSSSS
     I                                        9  140WSSDAT
     I                                        7  120WSSYM
     I                                        7  100WSSYYY
     I                                       11  120WSSMMM
     I                                       13  140WSSDDD
JW2  I                                        7  140WSDATE
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  32 LOT
     I                                        1   8 F3LOT1
     I                                        9  16 F3LOT2
     I                                       17  24 F3LOT3
     I                                       25  32 F3LOT
     I                                        1  32 ZLOT
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  11 XXKAN
     I                                        1   30J6ONDO
     I                                        4   62J6CO2P
     I                                        7  10 XXZETI
     I                                        1  10 XXBARC
     I                                       11  11 XXCHKD
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  15 W2KAN
     I                                        1   1 W2ZERO
     I                                        2   5 W2ZETI
     I                                        6  14 W2FIL
     I                                       15  15 W2CHKD
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1 240 QR
     I                                        1   3 QRID
     I                                        7  10 QRZETI
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   8 W3LOT
     I                                        1   7 W3LOT1
     I                                        8   8 W3CHKD
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   60W@YYMM
     I                                        1   40W@YYYY
     I                                        5   60W@MMMM
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  14 W@SHIN
     I                                        1   5 W@SHN1
     I                                        6   6 W@SHNA
     I                                        7  11 W@SHN2
     I                                       12  12 W@SHNB
     I                                       13  14 W@SHN3
     I            DS
     I                                        1  12 W@BARC
     I                                        1  11 W@BAR@
     I                                        1   60W@BAR1
     I                                        7  110W@BAR2
     I                                       12  12 W@BAR3
      *
     IMOLOT       DS                          5
     I                                        1  32 XLOT
     I                                       33  57 XFWLOT
